21:["$","p",null,{"className":"gov-disclaimer","style":{"marginTop":"32px"},"children":"Note: The National Creator Economy Bill 2026 has been passed by the Rajya Sabha and is awaiting Presidential Assent at the time of publication. Some provisions may be subject to rule-making before full implementation. SICE is being built in anticipation of, and in alignment with, the framework this legislation establishes."}]
